import React, { useState } from 'react' import { TableContainer,TableBody,TableHead,Table,TableRow,TableCell,TextField,Button,Paper } from '@material-ui/core' import Chart from '../../components/chart/Chart' const TAble = () => { const[subData,setSubData]=useState([]) const[finalData,setFinalData]=useState([]) function submitData(subData){ setFinalData(finalData=>[...finalData,subData]) setSubData(subData={}) } return (
setSubData({...subData,'sub':e.target.value})} label="name"/> setSubData({...subData,'sem':e.target.value})} label="time"/> {finalData.map((row,i) => ( {row.sub} {row.sem} ))}
) } export default TAble
